snippet.title: DRAGON BALL: Sparking! ZERO – Saiyan & Namek Sagas Character Trailer
snippet.description:
From Raditz's arrival on Earth to Frieza's invasion of Namek, it's been a ride.
Pre-Order DRAGON BALL: Sparking! ZERO: https://www.bnent.eu/PreorderDBSZ #dbsz 

The Music used in the video is not available in the base game.
It is included in a DLC Anime Song Pack sold separately.
